         h3 We are looking at the complete fight record of Floyd Mayweather -- The Undefeated Champ and chanllengers like -- Conor McGregor 
         br 
         h3  This program's information on the fighter's record contains: 
         p 
         ul
          li Name
          li Record 
          li Nationality
          li Website  
        h3 The Matches 
        p 
        u1 
          li Date of Fight 
          l1 Fighter 
          l1 Outcome 
        
         h2 Using the API

         h4 Get for how to Get the Fighters  
         p
         ul
          li GET http://localhost:1337/

         h4 Get for how to get one of the fighters 
         p
         ul
          li GET http://localhost:1337//fighter/:id"fighter"

         h4 Get for how to get the fighter by their name  
         p
         ul
          li GET http://localhost:1337/fighter/:name"name"

         h4 Get for the matches a fighter has been in 
         p 
         u1 
          l1 Get http://localhost:1337/match"match" 

         h4 Get for the matches id  
         p 
         u1 
          l1 Get http://localhost:1337/match/:identifier"Id" 

          h4 Get for the matches outcome  
          p 
          u1 
           l1 Get http://localhost:1337/outcome/:outcome"outcome" 

         h4 A Delete for a fighter that has lost to the champ 
         p
         ul
          li GET http://localhost:1337/delete/"id"

         h4 Adding the next fighter to the career record win for the champ 
         p
         ul
          li POST http://localhost:1337 { "fighter": "fighter name", "date": "fight date", "outcome": "fight outcome" }
